3\t| **Data** | 集成测试 | `*_integration_test.go` | 真实 DB |\n   674\t\n   675
\t### 11.2 Biz 层测试示例\n   676\t\n   677\t```go\n   678\t// internal/biz/wapi
/user_test.go\n   679\tpackage wapi\n   680\t\n   681\timport (\n   682\t    "co
ntext"\n   683\t    "testing"\n   684\t    \n   685\t    "github.com/stretchr/te
stify/assert"\n   686\t    "github.com/stretchr/testify/mock"\n   687\t    "new-
